data.description: Wow! Rare five bedroom home  in Waterville! Large eat in kitchen includes all appliances staying and is open to the family room with vaulted ceilings and cozy fireplace. Formal dining room with tray ceiling and beautiful hardwood floors.  Convenient First floor master suite featuring a separate tub and shower. Upstairs you will find four more bedrooms and a full bathroom. Entertain in the partially finished basement.  Furnace new as of January 2024.  Roof in 2018.  This one has it all and won't last, hurry!
